data.description: A must-see! This well maintained 3 beds, 2.5 bath house situated in a quiet cul-de-sac with open floor plan! Spacious kitchen and  breakfast area open to a large great room. Natural gas fireplace, contemporary breakfast ceiling light, fully fenced big and flat backyard back up to woods, which bring you a cozy and private life. Vaulted ceiling in primary bedroom upstairs with an open loft lended at the the end of staircase. No carpet! Brand new Vinyl Plank floor all over the whole house; newly installed granite countertop and faucet & garbage disposal as well. The roof is just replaced with architectural shingle that comes with a transferral warranty; freshly painted interior and power washed exterior.  Close to shops, restaurants, UNCC and malls. Near I-77 and 85, 20 minutes to uptown Charlotte!
